# De-identified Data
# ==================
# De-identified analysis datasets for manuscript preparation.
# All participant IDs replaced with SHA-256 hashed pseudonyms.
# All dates shifted to age-in-days offsets.
# Audit log generated for every transformation.
#
# Path: $NANO_DATA_ROOT/deidentified/
# See config/paths.yml and docs/hipaa_compliance_checklist.md
#
# WARNING: Even de-identified data should not be committed to git.
# Consult with PI and IRB before any data sharing.
